 QPS per machine
    MySQL / PostgreSQL
        1k QPS per machine
    MongoDB / Cassandra
        10k QPS
    Redis / Memcached
        100k ~ 1m QPS
        Memcached does not support permanent storage
            Memcached help to manage machine's memory

 You have to use Cache for Read Frequent Systems
    cache.set("this is a key", "this is a value");
    cache.set("foo", 1, ttl=60);
